# Local dev config (loaded automatically by `vite` / `npm run dev`).
#
# By default the globe + dashboard read the public snapshot — the same real data
# as production — so `npm run dev` works on its own with NO backend running.
#
# Comment this line out to use a locally-running API instead (start it with
# `make dev` or `make api`), e.g. to test backend changes like grid_load_mw that
# aren't in the published snapshot yet.
VITE_SNAPSHOT_URL=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/peterklingelhofer/carbonlens/data/snapshot.json
